file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: TODO list tram example view side service API
  license:
    name: MIT
servers:
  - url: 'http://light-tram.swagger.io/v1'
paths:
  /todoviews:
    get:
      summary: List of todo task by search
      operationId: listTodos
      tags:
        - todos
      parameters:
        - name: searchValue
          in: query
          description: search critiria
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
      security:
        - todo_auth:
            - 'read:todo'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: List of todos
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: array
                items:
                  $ref: '#/components/schemas/TodoView'
        default:
          description: unexpected error
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Error'
components:
  securitySchemes:
    todo_auth:
      type: oauth2
      description: This API uses OAuth 2 with the client credential grant flow.
      flows:
        clientCredentials:
          tokenUrl: 'https://localhost:6882/token'
          scopes:
            'write:todos': modify todo in your task list
            'read:todos': read your todo from your task list
  schemas:
    TodoView:
      required:
        - id
        - title
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
        title:
          type: string
        completed:
          type: boolean
        executionOrder:
          type: integer
          format: int32
    Error:
      required:
        - code
        - message
      properties:
        code:
          type: integer
          format: int32
        message:
          type: string
